LoxBerry Wiki pages are DokuWiki, not Markdown.

Required syntax rules:
- Headings only with `=` markers (for example `===== Abschnitt =====`).
- Links only as `[[url|text]]`.
- For parser-sensitive URL lines (especially `http://...`) prefer `%%...%%` literal blocks.
- Bullet list items begin with two spaces: `  * item`.
- Keep Version History inside `++++ Version History |` / closing `++++`.

Forbidden syntax:
- Markdown headings (`#`, `##`, ...)
- Triple-backtick fenced blocks
- Markdown links (`[text](url)`)

Checklist before finalizing wiki text:
1) No unresolved template placeholders (`{{...}}`).
2) No raw `http://` URL in normal prose where DokuWiki could parse `//` as italic.
3) Keep canonical sections present:
   - Überblick
   - Unterstützte Regionen
   - Integration über MQTT
   - Integration über HTTP
   - Fragen und Fehler melden
